[VT_ReportPascal] Unit Start/Finish Dates for Training Plans

When used in addition to the Sub-Query - First Linked Occurrence per Enrolled Unit or Sub-Query - Last Linked Occurrence per Enrolled

Unit SQL Sub-Queries, this allows the report to populate the Start/Finish Dates against Enrolled Units, used in

MasterData1's OnBeforePrint() Procedure, for Memo Fields named memStartDate and memEndDate.

First, this checks whether a Linked Occurrence Enrolment is connected to the Enrolled Unit, then returns the Occurrence Start/Finish

Dates if this criteria is met.

If not, refer to the Start/Finish Dates recorded in the Enrolment Results Wizard.

